  {
    "title": "Meta Mid laners",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "It is recommended that you practice each Mid lane hero at least once, so that you know enemy skill types, cooldowns, and learn matchups and recommended skill builds for different heroes."
          },
          {
            "text": "A Mid laner will determine the pick off and ganking routes (because mid laners usually rotate with the roamer)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "These heroes are currently meta and will dominate (most of the time as shown in tournaments) if you mastered them (In no particular order):"
          }
        ]
      }
